From: "Greg Lindahl" <lindahl@pbm.com>
In-Reply-To: <199610311924.LAA05056@rt.com> from "Rich Skrenta" at Oct 31, 96 11:24:57 am
X-Mailer: ELM [version 2.4 PL25]
Content-Type: text
Content-Length: 1210      
